Synopsis: 
The story revolves around Shirayuki, a beautiful girl working as a medicine woman who has red hair, which is very rare in her country. 
When she is proposed and chased after by the prince of her country, she runs away, only to meet Zen, the prince of a neighbouring country. 
Finding respect for the young man, she decides to serve at his side as his court doctor. 


